<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">The best journalistic accounts of Rumsfeld's reign at the Pentagon have been by Seymour Hersh, writing in the <i>New Yorker </i>magazine. You can read his articles <a href="http://www.newyorker.com/fact/content/articles/030512fa_fact" target="_blank">"Selective intelligence"</a> and <a href="http://www.newyorker.com/fact/content/articles/040517fa_fact2?040517fa_fact2" target="_blank">"Chain of command"</a> online.<p>
